               <p>I am a <rs id="t17740413-108-deflabel540" type="occupation">watch-case maker</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17740413-108-defend910 t17740413-108-deflabel540"></join> by trade; I called there that day to see them, not having much to do; sometimes I work in a smith's shop.</p>
